item.description:
@xnightmarepkz_rocks wrote:

I Never Needed To portforward in the first place. Use This - http://www.bittorrent.com/ And Once you have it downloaded, Open it.

Then, go to Options > Preferences , and put 43594 as the port.

If you havent Already, You Need To Make a no-ip here. http://www.no-ip.com/

I Dont Really Feel Like Explaining What to Do For No-ip. Its pretty Self-Explanatory.

Anyway, Bring Up your No-ip, And Bit-torrent, Your Server Should be Online. If you would like to Check it, Use this http://bit.ly/albJd1
